# defino funciones

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def f(x):
    y = np.sin(np.pi * np.log(x))
    return y

def punto_medio(a,b,h,f):
    x = np.arange(a,b,h)
    rm = np.sum(f(x+h/2))*h
    return rm

def trapecio(a,b,h,f):
    x = np.arange(a,b+h,h)
    rt = (h/2)*(f(x[0])+2*np.sum(f(x[1:-1]))+f(x[-1]))
    return rt

def simpson(a,b,h,f):
    x = np.arange(a,b+h,h)
    rs = (h/6)*(f(x[0])+4*np.sum(f(x[:-1]+h/2))+2*np.sum(f(x[1:-1]))+f(x[-1]))
    return rs

def gamma(x):
    y = (1/np.exp(x))*x**(1/2)
    return y

x_sup = np.arange(4,10.1,0.1)
h = np.arange(0.01,1.01,0.01)

aprox_gamma_medio = np.zeros((len(h), len(x_sup)))
aprox_gamma_trapecio = np.zeros((len(h), len(x_sup)))
aprox_gamma_simpson = np.zeros((len(h), len(x_sup)))

for i, x in enumerate(x_sup):
    for j, hi in enumerate(h):
        aprox_gamma_medio[j, i] = punto_medio(0, x, hi,gamma)
        aprox_gamma_trapecio[j, i] = trapecio(0, x, hi,gamma)
        aprox_gamma_simpson[j, i] = simpson(0, x, hi,gamma)


l=[aprox_gamma_medio.T,aprox_gamma_trapecio.T,aprox_gamma_simpson.T]
m=["Punto Medio","Trapecio","Simpson"]
n=np.arange(1,4,1)
plt.figure(figsize=(20,10))
plt.suptitle("Aproximación Númerica de $\Gamma(3/2)$ ")
for i,j,k in zip(l,n,m):
    plt.subplot(1,3,j)
    p=plt.pcolormesh(h,x_sup,i)
    plt.title(f'Método {k}')
    plt.xlabel('h')
    plt.ylabel('x_sup')
    plt.tight_layout()
plt.colorbar(p, label='Valor aproximado')
plt.show()

from scipy import special

error_medio = np.zeros((len(h), len(x_sup)))
error_trapecio = np.zeros((len(h), len(x_sup)))
error_simpson = np.zeros((len(h), len(x_sup)))

exacto = special.gamma(3/2)
for i, x in enumerate(x_sup):
    for j, hi in enumerate(h):
        aprox_medio = punto_medio(0, x, hi,gamma)
        aprox_trapecio = trapecio( 0, x, hi,gamma)
        aprox_simpson = simpson( 0, x, hi,gamma)
        
        error_medio[j, i] = np.abs(exacto - aprox_medio)
        error_trapecio[j, i] = np.abs(exacto - aprox_trapecio)
        error_simpson[j, i] = np.abs(exacto - aprox_simpson)
        

t=[error_medio,error_trapecio,error_simpson]
m=["Punto Medio","Trapecio","Simpson"]
n=np.arange(1,4,1)

plt.figure(figsize=(20,10))
for i,j,k in zip(t,m,n):
    plt.subplot(1,3,k)
    plt.imshow(i, extent=[4, 10, 0.01, 1], aspect='auto', origin='lower')
    plt.colorbar(label='Error')
    plt.title(f'Error del {j}')
    plt.xlabel('x_sup')
    plt.ylabel('h')
    plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
